fields.note: This place was awesome!!! Highly recommend for families of all sizes!

I have a child in a wheelchair and getting into the attraction was a little difficult. Luckily we had a lovely employee who helped us get in, eventually, and we were able to see the show. I would recommend better handicap access in the future. Show was great though once we got to see it!
This was a pretty cool attraction, but the lines were so long!
